Today marks 5 years since we lost 5 officers in the deadliest attack on law enforcement since September 11th. Today belongs to these men. 
Officer Ahrens, Officer Krol, Officer Smith, Officer Thompson, and Officer Zamarripa.

Those 5 brave officers were killed and 7 other officers wounded in an ambush during a Black Lives Matter protest in Dallas by a shooter who unabashedly set out to kill white cops. 

In a time when law enforcement has been demoralized, degraded, demonized and even defunded, it is more important than ever we honor those who lost their lives holding that thin blue line. #thinblueline #bluelivesmatter #dallas #teamTomi
